WEBVTT

01:52.370 --> 01:57.430
[The Legend of Rosy Clouds]

01:58.680 --> 02:01.910
[Episode 20]

02:02.010 --> 02:04.950
[Juyun Pavilion]

02:07.770 --> 02:08.690
Fan Yun,

02:09.560 --> 02:10.729
this generous...

02:11.170 --> 02:13.120
friend of yours,

02:15.080 --> 02:16.310
do I know him?

02:22.030 --> 02:22.710
Yes,

02:23.380 --> 02:24.400
you do know him.

02:25.040 --> 02:26.320
Take a closer look.

02:28.760 --> 02:29.480
Zheng?

02:31.910 --> 02:33.440
You really recognized him?

02:35.920 --> 02:36.560
See?

02:37.310 --> 02:39.310
Even Tian Xing could recognize you.

02:39.800 --> 02:40.710
I don't know why you spend

02:40.710 --> 02:42.540
so much time disguising yourself

02:42.540 --> 02:44.000
every day.

02:44.870 --> 02:45.670
That's right.

02:46.040 --> 02:46.650
Zheng.

02:47.970 --> 02:49.100
Young Master Qiyan.

02:50.079 --> 02:51.030
Well,

02:51.470 --> 02:53.130
thanks for treating us today.

02:53.430 --> 02:55.310
Eat whatever you want today.

02:55.840 --> 02:57.600
It's not like the mansion,
with all its rules,

02:57.600 --> 02:59.440
and there's no one here to upset you.

02:59.440 --> 03:01.970
The most important thing today
is to be happy.

03:02.780 --> 03:03.280
Eat up.

03:07.420 --> 03:08.060
Alright.

03:08.980 --> 03:09.910
Here, Tian Xing.

03:11.970 --> 03:12.650
Since

03:12.670 --> 03:14.080
Young Master Qiyan is so hospitable,

03:14.080 --> 03:15.630
let's not let him down.

03:16.079 --> 03:16.560
Eat up.

03:22.620 --> 03:23.100
Come on.

03:26.340 --> 03:27.450
Thank you, Young Master Qiyan.

03:27.450 --> 03:28.050
Eat more.

03:32.870 --> 03:34.810
You're really enjoying your food
this time.

03:34.810 --> 03:36.350
The things I sent to the mansion

03:36.350 --> 03:37.410
were all returned.

03:37.760 --> 03:38.930
In the mansion,

03:39.040 --> 03:40.590
of course we can't get special treatment.

03:40.590 --> 03:41.560
If we do that,

03:41.560 --> 03:43.420
we have to bear the consequences.

03:43.510 --> 03:44.820
It's different outside the mansion.

03:44.820 --> 03:47.870
Out here, everyone earns their keep
through their own abilities.

03:47.870 --> 03:49.329
You take things in stride.

03:50.150 --> 03:51.220
Young Master Qiyan,

03:51.220 --> 03:53.280
where's the thing you promised to show me?

03:53.280 --> 03:54.280
Let's eat first.

03:54.630 --> 03:56.430
Nothing should delay a meal.

03:56.760 --> 03:57.990
I haven't seen you for a few days,

03:57.990 --> 03:59.520
and you've gotten thinner.

04:01.840 --> 04:02.560
But...

04:02.560 --> 04:04.890
I'll show it to you
when you finish eating.

04:08.110 --> 04:08.780
Alright.

04:09.340 --> 04:10.580
Once I'm done eating,

04:10.580 --> 04:11.780
you must show it to me.

04:30.060 --> 04:31.030
I'm full.

04:35.620 --> 04:36.870
I'm really full.

04:44.700 --> 04:45.470
Well...

04:45.470 --> 04:47.400
There's more, Young Master Qiyan?

04:48.350 --> 04:48.740
I...

04:48.740 --> 04:50.300
really can't eat anymore.

04:50.300 --> 04:51.500
Tian Xing, you eat it.

04:51.820 --> 04:53.350
I can't eat anymore either.

04:54.700 --> 04:56.159
We both can't eat anymore.

04:56.470 --> 04:57.740
I think you can.

05:05.550 --> 05:07.140
So it's an account book?

05:18.610 --> 05:20.940
There's nothing wrong with these totals.

05:22.940 --> 05:24.260
Could it be that...

05:24.940 --> 05:26.590
there's nothing wrong with

05:27.430 --> 05:29.890
the Services Bureau's
account book either?

05:30.180 --> 05:31.300
I told you before

05:31.300 --> 05:33.700
that there's no problem with the accounts.

05:38.909 --> 05:40.670
But the unit prices on this

05:40.940 --> 05:43.070
are a bit higher than the market price.

05:43.590 --> 05:45.670
What was the Services Bureau thinking,

05:45.670 --> 05:46.909
spending so much money

05:46.909 --> 05:48.110
to buy these things?

05:48.670 --> 05:50.590
The Services Bureau
wasn't spending its own money,

05:50.590 --> 05:52.920
so of course they didn't
feel bad about it.

05:56.790 --> 05:57.990
So that's why

05:58.350 --> 06:00.470
you raised the prices

06:01.060 --> 06:03.030
to profit from the Qi Residence?

06:06.470 --> 06:09.000
Why shouldn't I profit
from the Qi Residence?

06:09.180 --> 06:10.470
I am just a merchant.

06:10.950 --> 06:12.210
If people want to buy things,

06:12.210 --> 06:14.140
I have no reason not to sell to them.

06:16.300 --> 06:18.350
You suspect there's something wrong
with the Services Bureau,

06:18.350 --> 06:19.940
that they're corrupt.

06:20.590 --> 06:23.650
I'm afraid you might be
looking in the wrong direction.

06:38.430 --> 06:39.790
Your Excellency.

06:39.790 --> 06:41.500
These are local specialties

06:41.500 --> 06:43.470
we brothers specially brought for you

06:43.470 --> 06:44.820
from Yong City.

06:45.140 --> 06:47.390
There are round dates,

06:47.990 --> 06:49.940
delicious dried meat,

06:50.140 --> 06:52.470
and dried lily bulbs.

07:00.590 --> 07:01.870
Great!

07:02.590 --> 07:04.060
I am very pleased!

07:04.740 --> 07:06.070
Hurry up and have a seat.

07:10.820 --> 07:12.060
Could you tell me

07:12.060 --> 07:13.870
how things are

07:13.870 --> 07:15.230
in Yong City

07:15.230 --> 07:16.300
recently?

07:17.260 --> 07:18.380
Your Excellency.

07:19.060 --> 07:20.300
It's terrible.

07:20.870 --> 07:22.350
When we left,

07:22.440 --> 07:24.350
Yong City was suffering from a plague.

07:24.350 --> 07:26.160
We don't know what's going on,

07:26.470 --> 07:29.350
but people are dying in droves.

07:29.350 --> 07:31.450
We really couldn't bear it anymore.

07:31.620 --> 07:34.380
We came specially
to ask you to find a solution.

07:34.380 --> 07:35.700
To see if you could

07:35.700 --> 07:37.430
appoint a capable person

07:37.430 --> 07:39.909
to save the people of Yong City.

07:40.560 --> 07:42.220
About the plague in Yong City,

07:42.290 --> 07:44.080
I've already received the memorial.

07:44.080 --> 07:44.880
Rest assured.

07:45.390 --> 07:46.990
I will definitely find a way.

07:47.110 --> 07:48.110
Your Excellency.

07:48.110 --> 07:49.670
You mustn't fool us.

07:49.670 --> 07:50.790
I promise.

07:52.140 --> 07:53.650
You came from far away today.

07:53.650 --> 07:54.650
You must be tired.

07:55.030 --> 07:56.690
Come on, here's a toast to you.

07:57.060 --> 07:58.170
May our Yong City

07:58.350 --> 07:59.670
return to normal as soon as possible,

07:59.670 --> 08:01.000
with no more disasters.

08:02.140 --> 08:05.030
Thank you, Your Excellency, for keeping
the people of Yong City in your thoughts.

08:05.030 --> 08:07.380
We're not leaving
until we've had our fill today.

08:07.380 --> 08:07.790
Come on.

08:07.790 --> 08:08.590
If you don't get drunk,

08:08.590 --> 08:10.240
it means you look down on us!

08:10.790 --> 08:12.470
And the Shi family!

08:13.350 --> 08:14.230
If you don't get drunk,

08:14.230 --> 08:16.890
it means you look down
on the nobles of Yong City.

08:20.550 --> 08:22.820
The Shi family
is indeed very straightforward.

08:22.820 --> 08:23.810
Well then...

08:27.500 --> 08:29.140
I can't fall behind, right?

08:29.700 --> 08:30.260
Come on!

08:30.500 --> 08:31.740
We're not leaving
until we've had our fill today!

08:31.740 --> 08:34.470
We're not leaving
until we've had our fill today!

08:42.309 --> 08:43.309
Your Excellency,

08:43.539 --> 08:44.800
can you keep drinking?

08:45.020 --> 08:46.620
Are you kidding?

08:46.620 --> 08:47.710
My drinking capacity

08:47.710 --> 08:49.990
is one of the best in the Nine Cities!

08:49.990 --> 08:50.900
Keep drinking!

08:50.900 --> 08:53.300
We're not leaving
until we've had our fill!

09:02.230 --> 09:04.020
The wine in Ling'an

09:04.420 --> 09:05.990
is indeed good.

09:07.380 --> 09:08.900
What is that thing?

09:10.020 --> 09:11.540
What?

09:20.660 --> 09:22.020
Isn't this the Governor?

09:22.020 --> 09:23.110
How can you call him a thing?

09:23.110 --> 09:24.070
What are you talking about?

09:24.070 --> 09:25.950
Are you insulting His Excellency?

09:25.950 --> 09:27.480
What are you talking about?

09:28.190 --> 09:31.110
Drink up... Drink up...

09:31.110 --> 09:32.990
Four of us drinking against one—

09:33.060 --> 09:34.570
isn't it a bit of bullying?

09:35.140 --> 09:38.230
It seems His Excellency has been
hiding his drinking ability.

09:38.230 --> 09:40.520
You have to be honest when drinking.

09:40.660 --> 09:42.260
It seems His Excellency

09:42.260 --> 09:44.190
is quite sincere to us, right?

09:44.780 --> 09:46.990
His Excellency is like this already.

09:46.990 --> 09:48.830
He must be drunk.

09:48.830 --> 09:50.500
Let's go back and rest first.

09:51.140 --> 09:51.990
We'll...

09:52.830 --> 09:54.420
We'll come back later.

09:54.900 --> 09:56.430
What about His Excellency?

09:57.210 --> 09:58.070
What about him?

10:00.190 --> 10:02.110
The floor is nice and cool.

10:02.110 --> 10:03.740
His Excellency can rest here.

10:03.740 --> 10:04.740
Just leave him be.

10:05.500 --> 10:06.500
Will that be okay?

10:07.350 --> 10:08.870
Yes.

10:08.870 --> 10:10.110
Alright then.

10:10.110 --> 10:11.070
Let's go.

10:12.070 --> 10:13.780
Your Excellency, we're leaving.

10:13.780 --> 10:15.380
Let's go.

10:33.530 --> 10:34.790
Your Excellency? Your Excellency?

10:34.790 --> 10:36.070
Are you alright?

10:38.110 --> 10:40.190
Hurry up and call Lord Wei
and the others over.

10:40.190 --> 10:41.900
Tell them
there are important matters to discuss.

10:41.900 --> 10:42.500
Yes.

10:47.830 --> 10:49.490
I haven't acted in a long time.

10:50.110 --> 10:51.660
I'm really out of practice.

10:56.160 --> 10:57.640
Go burn some mugwort.

11:01.110 --> 11:02.100
Father!

11:02.260 --> 11:03.520
Mother!

11:04.110 --> 11:07.500
Father! Mother!

11:07.500 --> 11:08.590
Young Masters,

11:08.610 --> 11:09.930
please don't get too close.

11:09.930 --> 11:11.000
Please stop.

11:11.440 --> 11:12.810
Father! Mother!

11:12.870 --> 11:14.230
Lord Jiang, get out of the way!

11:14.230 --> 11:15.620
Let me see my parents!

11:15.620 --> 11:17.080
When your parents were brought here,

11:17.080 --> 11:18.410
it was already too late.

11:27.190 --> 11:28.260
Young Masters,

11:28.310 --> 11:29.380
my condolences.

11:30.590 --> 11:31.990
Could we talk in private?

11:32.140 --> 11:33.230
What did you say?

11:33.360 --> 11:35.420
Our parents' bodies are barely cold,

11:35.420 --> 11:37.780
and you, Jiang Shu, want to cremate them?

11:38.520 --> 11:39.900
In Yong City, since ancient times,

11:39.900 --> 11:41.590
we believe in burying the dead!

11:41.590 --> 11:42.770
How can you just cremate them?

11:42.770 --> 11:43.700
In your dreams!

11:44.540 --> 11:46.600
Everyone, please listen to me first.

11:46.990 --> 11:49.590
I heard the epidemic in Yong City
is severe now.

11:49.800 --> 11:50.530
Your parents

11:50.550 --> 11:52.410
died because they were infected.

11:53.260 --> 11:55.260
If they are not cremated on the spot,

11:55.260 --> 11:56.870
I'm afraid the whole Ling'an City

11:56.870 --> 11:58.470
will be in danger.

11:58.470 --> 11:59.540
No, no, no.

11:59.540 --> 12:00.540
Absolutely not.

12:04.830 --> 12:05.650
Then I

12:05.920 --> 12:07.070
will go work on

12:07.100 --> 12:09.630
a prescription for the epidemic
in Yong City.

12:09.830 --> 12:10.780
You may leave.

12:11.420 --> 12:12.550
I will take my leave.

12:30.330 --> 12:31.990
Greetings, Your Excellency.

12:35.950 --> 12:37.610
Lord Lu came to complain to me,

12:38.450 --> 12:40.850
saying he didn't see you
all day yesterday.

12:41.260 --> 12:42.660
He wants me to punish you.

12:43.900 --> 12:46.230
Are you willing to accept the punishment?

12:52.950 --> 12:53.870
I am.

12:54.950 --> 12:55.530
Good.

12:57.570 --> 12:58.900
Then I'll punish you...

13:01.210 --> 13:02.540
by making you talk to me.

13:19.900 --> 13:20.660
It feels like

13:21.950 --> 13:23.750
we haven't talked in a long time.

13:45.140 --> 13:46.350
Do you have nothing

13:47.140 --> 13:48.380
you want to say to me?

13:50.950 --> 13:51.710
I...

13:52.500 --> 13:54.100
It's not that I don't want to.

13:54.710 --> 13:55.710
I just can't.

14:00.780 --> 14:01.620
Alright.

14:05.990 --> 14:07.350
Then tell me,

14:07.850 --> 14:09.850
what have you been busy with lately?

14:11.450 --> 14:13.830
We've been investigating
the Services Bureau.

14:13.830 --> 14:14.540
I know.

14:15.540 --> 14:17.660
The Services Bureau reported yesterday,

14:17.660 --> 14:19.230
requesting a hearing tomorrow

14:19.230 --> 14:20.160
to confront you.

14:20.540 --> 14:22.170
If it's proven
that you made a false accusation,

14:22.170 --> 14:23.500
you could be convicted.

14:25.850 --> 14:27.610
The hearing is tomorrow?

14:29.140 --> 14:30.020
The day before yesterday,

14:30.020 --> 14:32.110
we went to the Services Bureau
to sort out documents

14:32.110 --> 14:34.380
and found discrepancies in the accounts.

14:34.380 --> 14:36.380
We investigated all day yesterday,

14:36.380 --> 14:38.070
but found no problems.

14:39.020 --> 14:40.070
If...

14:40.770 --> 14:43.170
we still can't find any evidence tomorrow,

14:43.420 --> 14:43.990
then...

14:46.830 --> 14:48.630
Where did you go to investigate?

14:49.110 --> 14:50.070
Juyun Pavilion.

14:51.420 --> 14:53.020
You investigated Lou Qiyan?

14:53.870 --> 14:54.710
However...

14:55.260 --> 14:56.260
we found nothing.

15:00.710 --> 15:03.110
Looks like you have to keep investigating.

15:04.940 --> 15:05.690
Your Excellency,

15:05.690 --> 15:06.840
don't you want to ask

15:07.190 --> 15:08.870
why I investigated him?

15:11.420 --> 15:14.620
Of course it's because
there's something wrong with him.

15:15.030 --> 15:16.250
It's not him.

15:16.310 --> 15:17.770
It's the Services Bureau.

15:18.780 --> 15:19.490
But...

15:20.660 --> 15:23.620
even though we know there's something
wrong with the Services Bureau,

15:23.620 --> 15:25.480
we still couldn't find anything.

15:30.500 --> 15:31.660
Have you forgotten

15:32.440 --> 15:33.250
who you are?

15:43.020 --> 15:43.810
Right.

15:44.540 --> 15:46.340
You are right, Your Excellency.

15:46.380 --> 15:49.070
I am just a probationary civil official.

15:49.540 --> 15:51.870
I have no right
to investigate the Services Bureau.

15:51.870 --> 15:53.230
That's not what I meant.

15:54.020 --> 15:55.230
I mean,

15:55.230 --> 15:57.020
before you married into the manor,

15:57.020 --> 15:58.680
you were very well-informed.

15:59.110 --> 16:01.780
If investigating as an official
yields nothing,

16:01.780 --> 16:03.700
why not try another identity?

16:04.110 --> 16:06.040
You might get unexpected results.

16:12.990 --> 16:14.140
Right.

16:14.140 --> 16:15.740
Why didn't I think of that?

16:17.110 --> 16:19.640
Thank you for the reminder,
Your Excellency.

16:19.720 --> 16:20.410
Alright.

16:20.440 --> 16:21.900
Don't be so polite with me.

16:26.350 --> 16:27.020
Right.

16:28.930 --> 16:30.330
I have something for you.

16:30.500 --> 16:31.420
What is it?

16:38.110 --> 16:39.460
This.

16:42.230 --> 16:43.660
What is this?

16:45.370 --> 16:46.400
I carved this

16:46.420 --> 16:47.540
myself.

16:48.620 --> 16:49.500
No.

16:51.310 --> 16:52.840
I picked it up on the street.

16:53.020 --> 16:54.020
On the street?

16:54.050 --> 16:55.450
That's not right either.

16:55.960 --> 16:57.540
I just want to give it to you.

16:57.540 --> 16:59.340
There's no reason. Just take it.

17:08.550 --> 17:09.460
Say no more.

17:10.550 --> 17:11.680
Go back to your work.

17:13.270 --> 17:13.829
Alright.

17:14.220 --> 17:15.030
Well...

17:15.869 --> 17:17.130
yes, Your Excellency.

17:22.869 --> 17:24.109
Remember to wear it!

17:32.510 --> 17:33.310
Lord Cai!

17:33.310 --> 17:34.980
Our parents died of the plague!

17:34.980 --> 17:36.700
Yet you haven't given us an explanation!

17:36.700 --> 17:37.510
Give us an explanation!

17:37.510 --> 17:40.270
How will you handle this?

17:40.270 --> 17:41.380
How?

17:43.870 --> 17:45.270
Alright! Alright!

17:45.270 --> 17:47.220
Stop shouting, will you?

17:48.010 --> 17:50.290
You're deafening me!

17:53.140 --> 17:54.900
As the saying goes,

17:54.900 --> 17:56.940
every wrong has its cause,
and every debt its debtor.

17:56.940 --> 18:00.370
If you want revenge,
figure out who to target first.

18:00.660 --> 18:02.660
We brothers have been here for days.

18:03.420 --> 18:05.980
They say ever since
the Nine Cities made history

18:05.980 --> 18:08.140
by appointing a little girl
as an official,

18:08.140 --> 18:10.380
the world hasn't been peaceful!

18:10.380 --> 18:11.110
How could it be peaceful?

18:11.110 --> 18:12.030
There's a plague now!

18:12.030 --> 18:13.070
It must be that female official

18:13.070 --> 18:14.110
who angered the Spirit Immortal,

18:14.110 --> 18:14.870
bringing disaster to Yong City.

18:14.870 --> 18:16.270
Exactly! Is that right?

18:16.270 --> 18:17.850
So you mean

18:18.140 --> 18:20.310
there's a problem with Fan Yun?

18:20.870 --> 18:23.420
So the little girl is called Fan Yun?

18:29.900 --> 18:31.220
-Did I say that?
-Fan Yun?

18:31.220 --> 18:33.150
That little girl is called Fan Yun?

18:34.070 --> 18:35.340
Come on, Lord Cai.

18:35.600 --> 18:38.070
You can trust the four of us brothers.

18:38.520 --> 18:40.510
Just tell us clearly what's going on.

18:40.510 --> 18:41.510
Exactly.

18:41.510 --> 18:42.700
Tell us clearly.

18:47.460 --> 18:50.510
I understand how you feel.

18:51.070 --> 18:53.000
The most important thing right now

18:53.180 --> 18:57.660
is to have the Governor send someone
to Yong City to control the epidemic.

18:57.660 --> 19:00.570
That is the most urgent matter at hand.

19:00.830 --> 19:01.870
Lord Cai.

19:01.870 --> 19:02.750
Who do you think the Governor

19:02.750 --> 19:05.620
will send to Yong City?

19:05.620 --> 19:08.910
It doesn't matter who he sends.

19:09.380 --> 19:12.160
What matters is whether

19:12.310 --> 19:14.400
you can keep this person.

19:14.740 --> 19:16.310
What do you mean by that?

19:17.870 --> 19:18.600
Think about it.

19:18.600 --> 19:20.870
The person the Governor is going to send

19:20.870 --> 19:23.030
will eventually return, won't they?

19:24.070 --> 19:25.070
But if

19:25.070 --> 19:27.380
you take one of your own people back

19:27.380 --> 19:29.510
and let him stay in Yong City in the end,

19:30.140 --> 19:31.460
wouldn't that
solve the problem once and for all?

19:31.460 --> 19:32.760
Where can we find one of our own?

19:32.760 --> 19:33.700
One of our own?

19:33.700 --> 19:34.380
Wait.

19:34.380 --> 19:36.070
Where can we find one of our own?

19:36.070 --> 19:37.790
If we could find one of our own
to stay in Yong City,

19:37.790 --> 19:38.900
that would be best.

19:38.900 --> 19:41.030
The problem is where to find this leader.

19:41.030 --> 19:43.460
Yeah, where can we find this leader?

19:44.620 --> 19:45.660
I actually have

19:45.660 --> 19:47.940
an ideal candidate in mind.

19:47.940 --> 19:49.420
I just don't know

19:49.750 --> 19:51.030
if you four

19:51.420 --> 19:53.030
will agree to it.

19:58.460 --> 19:59.460
Tell us.

20:03.550 --> 20:06.410
Tian Xing, the top candidate
in the selection exam.

20:07.250 --> 20:09.690
Isn't he from Yong City?

20:12.540 --> 20:14.400
-He's from Yong City?
-Tian Xing?

20:15.680 --> 20:18.170
[Ume Tea Shop]

20:22.350 --> 20:24.030
Tomorrow is the hearing.

20:24.900 --> 20:26.100
We've had enough tea.

20:26.510 --> 20:29.840
Let's hurry up and keep investigating
the Services Bureau.

20:29.870 --> 20:30.950
We are

20:31.870 --> 20:33.110
investigating right now.

20:33.110 --> 20:34.140
And this place

20:34.140 --> 20:35.220
is the best spot

20:35.220 --> 20:36.350
to get information.

20:36.700 --> 20:37.510
Look.

20:37.570 --> 20:38.620
If

20:38.750 --> 20:40.700
the Services Bureau
really embezzled money,

20:40.700 --> 20:42.300
it must not be a small amount.

20:43.940 --> 20:45.030
If he hid the money

20:45.030 --> 20:46.110
at home,

20:46.110 --> 20:47.620
it would be easily found,

20:47.620 --> 20:49.110
and he wouldn't be able to deny it.

20:49.110 --> 20:49.830
Right.

20:49.830 --> 20:51.270
So I guess

20:51.270 --> 20:53.420
he must have hidden it in a secret place.

20:53.420 --> 20:54.620
Then let's not waste time.

20:54.620 --> 20:56.080
Let's hurry up and find it.

20:56.180 --> 20:57.380
No rush.

20:58.700 --> 20:59.750
Let me ask you.

20:59.750 --> 21:01.310
If

21:01.310 --> 21:03.420
you embezzled a large sum of money,

21:03.420 --> 21:04.580
and you couldn't

21:04.600 --> 21:06.600
move it out of the city any time soon,

21:06.660 --> 21:07.980
where would you hide it?

21:07.980 --> 21:10.710
A place with as few people as possible,
of course.

21:11.030 --> 21:12.030
I was born and raised

21:12.030 --> 21:13.690
in this Ling'an City.

21:14.350 --> 21:15.590
I am

21:16.790 --> 21:18.310
quite familiar with it here.

21:18.310 --> 21:20.140
The eastern suburb is bustling.

21:20.140 --> 21:22.700
The western suburb
has many government offices.

21:22.700 --> 21:25.500
The northern suburb
is heavily guarded by troops.

21:25.750 --> 21:27.980
Only the southern suburb is deserted.

21:29.030 --> 21:29.640
Then why

21:29.660 --> 21:31.320
don't we hurry up and go there?

21:32.340 --> 21:33.110
No.

21:34.070 --> 21:36.060
We can't search house by house.

21:36.380 --> 21:37.660
If we alert them

21:37.660 --> 21:38.900
and they change locations,

21:38.900 --> 21:40.700
it'll be hard for us to find them.

21:42.180 --> 21:43.910
Like a faint trail in the grass,

21:44.140 --> 21:46.000
there are always clues to follow.

21:47.140 --> 21:49.200
There are quite a lot of people today.

21:50.270 --> 21:51.460
Everyone is on time.

21:52.140 --> 21:53.030
Alright then.

21:54.700 --> 21:55.910
In this city,

21:56.420 --> 21:57.870
he is the most

21:59.920 --> 22:01.250
well-informed person.

22:01.510 --> 22:03.070
Let me tell you...

22:03.070 --> 22:04.030
Sir!

22:04.380 --> 22:05.270
Do you have any

22:05.270 --> 22:06.940
stories we haven't heard?

22:06.940 --> 22:09.510
Like...

22:09.510 --> 22:11.350
any stories about the southern suburb?

22:11.350 --> 22:14.150
You want to hear a story
about the southern suburb?

22:14.830 --> 22:15.360
Alright!

22:15.660 --> 22:16.870
In that case,

22:18.420 --> 22:19.350
today,

22:19.350 --> 22:21.070
I will tell you

22:21.070 --> 22:22.260
a strange tale

22:22.510 --> 22:23.970
from the southern suburb.

22:25.380 --> 22:26.980
To the south of Ling'an City,

22:27.750 --> 22:29.630
there is an isolated house.

22:30.590 --> 22:32.420
It has been uninhabited for years

22:32.420 --> 22:33.980
and abandoned long ago.

22:35.380 --> 22:37.660
Recently, this abandoned house

22:37.660 --> 22:39.720
has suddenly been said to be haunted.

22:56.310 --> 22:57.180
It's okay.

22:57.620 --> 22:58.610
Don't be afraid.

22:58.750 --> 23:00.310
It was a cat.

23:06.030 --> 23:06.790
Tian Xing.

23:07.220 --> 23:08.660
Are...

23:09.380 --> 23:10.110
you...

23:10.110 --> 23:11.700
scared?

23:13.270 --> 23:14.830
I... I am.

23:18.420 --> 23:19.510
It's okay.

23:20.280 --> 23:21.450
I'm scared too.

23:22.550 --> 23:23.660
Well...

23:24.620 --> 23:25.550
maybe...

23:25.550 --> 23:26.310
we...

23:27.750 --> 23:28.590
should...

23:29.590 --> 23:30.750
just go inside?

23:36.480 --> 23:37.800
Okay.

23:40.790 --> 23:41.830
I'll protect you.

23:44.620 --> 23:46.070
Walk behind me.

23:49.180 --> 23:50.110
Watch out.

23:54.590 --> 23:55.220
Fan Yun,

23:55.590 --> 23:56.590
are you done?

23:57.070 --> 23:58.380
Just a moment.

24:01.180 --> 24:02.080
Are you done?

24:02.270 --> 24:02.850
Yes.

24:03.350 --> 24:04.070
Let's go.

24:07.350 --> 24:08.010
Be careful.

24:21.030 --> 24:22.030
Go in.

24:33.870 --> 24:34.660
Hold this.

24:59.660 --> 25:00.790
Let's go, Tian Xing.

25:01.310 --> 25:02.220
Let's go.

25:04.070 --> 25:05.070
Watch your step.

25:06.140 --> 25:06.980
Be careful.

25:25.900 --> 25:26.610
Tian Xing,

25:27.420 --> 25:28.310
did you just see

25:28.310 --> 25:29.750
something fly by?

25:30.070 --> 25:30.890
I...

25:31.270 --> 25:32.340
didn't.

25:37.660 --> 25:38.620
Let's go.

25:39.510 --> 25:40.310
Let's go.

25:57.660 --> 25:58.180
Fan Yun!

25:58.180 --> 25:58.940
Let's go!

25:58.940 --> 25:59.940
Let's go!

25:59.940 --> 26:00.900
Wait, Tian Xing.

26:00.900 --> 26:02.070
Wait.

26:03.070 --> 26:04.270
I dropped my hairpin.

26:04.830 --> 26:06.140
Let's go! Hurry!

26:06.140 --> 26:07.110
Tian Xing,

26:08.110 --> 26:08.980
listen to me.

26:10.140 --> 26:11.490
Even if there are ghosts,

26:11.490 --> 26:13.020
we've already been scared.

26:13.270 --> 26:14.980
It'd be a waste to leave now.

26:40.790 --> 26:42.170
It's so spooky.

26:42.790 --> 26:43.670
Yeah.

26:44.460 --> 26:45.460
Tian Xing,

26:46.180 --> 26:47.620
let's look around first.

26:48.030 --> 26:48.790
Okay.

26:52.750 --> 26:53.680
Are you alright?

26:54.900 --> 26:55.750
I...

26:55.750 --> 26:56.590
I'm fine.

27:01.700 --> 27:03.640
Why is it so dark in here?

27:24.070 --> 27:24.960
Tian Xing,

27:25.550 --> 27:27.280
let's go inside and take a look.

27:28.420 --> 27:29.180
Tian...

27:33.790 --> 27:34.620
Tian Xing?

27:35.310 --> 27:36.270
Tian Xing!

27:38.220 --> 27:39.140
Who is it?

27:40.350 --> 27:41.420
Who's there?

27:44.910 --> 27:46.060
Who's there?

28:03.590 --> 28:04.850
Don't come any closer!

28:14.620 --> 28:15.190
Let...

28:15.210 --> 28:16.290
Let go!

28:16.750 --> 28:17.380
Let go!

28:19.550 --> 28:21.420
I'll kill you! I'll kill you!

28:22.460 --> 28:23.420
I'll kill you!

28:23.930 --> 28:24.930
Help!

28:27.830 --> 28:30.140
-There's a ghost!
-A ghost!

28:34.400 --> 28:37.210
Fan Yun...

28:39.680 --> 28:40.380
Don't be afraid.

28:40.380 --> 28:41.180
It's me.

28:45.660 --> 28:46.620
Tian Xing?

28:47.310 --> 28:47.900
Why...

28:48.180 --> 28:49.400
Why are you dressed like this?

28:49.400 --> 28:50.420
To fight fire with fire.

28:50.420 --> 28:51.790
They were the ones dressing up as ghosts,

28:51.790 --> 28:53.180
but ended up running away themselves.

28:53.180 --> 28:53.980
Hilarious.

28:53.980 --> 28:54.870
Dressing up...

28:55.110 --> 28:56.030
as ghosts?

28:58.830 --> 29:00.380
So you're actually the one who's young

29:00.380 --> 29:01.660
and brave.

29:01.660 --> 29:02.520
I'm flattered.

29:02.970 --> 29:03.610
However...

29:03.610 --> 29:05.140
according to what you said,

29:05.180 --> 29:06.510
these people

29:06.510 --> 29:08.840
went to great lengths
to dress up as ghosts

29:09.180 --> 29:11.030
just to keep others away from here.

29:11.030 --> 29:12.070
In that case,

29:12.070 --> 29:12.900
there must be something wrong

29:12.900 --> 29:14.030
with this place.

29:15.260 --> 29:16.180
Then we...

29:16.790 --> 29:17.790
shouldn't delay.

29:18.180 --> 29:18.830
Let's go.

29:22.380 --> 29:23.220
Tian Xing.

29:23.940 --> 29:25.140
I found nothing here.

29:25.140 --> 29:26.000
What about you?

29:26.180 --> 29:26.980
Nothing.

29:31.740 --> 29:33.370
Now there's only this coffin

29:33.460 --> 29:34.750
we haven't checked.

29:47.680 --> 29:49.200
How come there's nothing?

29:50.310 --> 29:51.030
Right.

29:52.140 --> 29:53.510
Then why did they dress up as ghosts

29:53.510 --> 29:54.710
and not let people in?

29:55.460 --> 29:57.590
This house looks dilapidated.

29:58.900 --> 30:01.070
But this coffin is quite new,

30:01.070 --> 30:02.420
and it's made

30:02.420 --> 30:03.700
of fine wood.

30:04.270 --> 30:05.330
It's possible that

30:05.570 --> 30:08.100
there are some places
we haven't checked yet.

30:21.510 --> 30:22.260
Tian Xing,

30:22.550 --> 30:23.380
look.

30:25.310 --> 30:28.370
There are marks
of long-term pushing and pulling here.

30:31.220 --> 30:32.820
There are some over here too.

30:33.660 --> 30:34.460
Let's move it.

30:49.030 --> 30:50.380
So much money?

30:55.700 --> 30:58.960
Isn't this my congratulatory gold
for the selection exam?

30:59.350 --> 31:01.530
The money embezzled by the Services Bureau

31:01.530 --> 31:02.790
is indeed hidden here.

31:03.290 --> 31:04.120
Tian Xing,

31:04.350 --> 31:05.510
let's return to the manor immediately

31:05.510 --> 31:07.170
and report it to the Governor.

31:14.900 --> 31:15.660
Fan Yun.

31:15.660 --> 31:17.190
Why are you walking so fast?

31:17.790 --> 31:18.680
Hurry up.

31:18.940 --> 31:21.110
We just found evidence
of the Services Bureau's corruption,

31:21.110 --> 31:22.570
and I feel uneasy about it.

31:22.590 --> 31:24.320
We'd better head back quickly.

31:37.180 --> 31:37.980
Sir...

31:39.610 --> 31:40.840
We won't move.

31:53.310 --> 31:54.310
Your Excellency.

31:54.750 --> 31:55.750
Your Excellency.

31:56.790 --> 31:57.550
How is it?

31:57.550 --> 31:59.140
It seems there's only one person inside.

31:59.140 --> 31:59.870
Okay.

32:03.070 --> 32:04.400
Why are you two going in?

32:04.520 --> 32:05.720
Guard the door for me.

32:15.460 --> 32:16.270
Fan...

32:20.060 --> 32:22.320
I'm Bo Qin. Greetings, Your Excellency.

32:25.550 --> 32:26.700
Oh, it's you.

32:26.700 --> 32:27.900
Why are you here?

32:27.900 --> 32:30.560
Lord Lu asked me
to organize the documents here.

32:32.750 --> 32:34.980
Have you seen Fan Yun and Tian Xing?

32:35.870 --> 32:37.220
No, I haven't.

32:37.870 --> 32:38.550
Alright.

32:38.940 --> 32:40.140
Get back to your work.

32:40.140 --> 32:40.620
Yes.

32:49.510 --> 32:51.310
It's this late, and Fan Yun isn't back.

32:51.310 --> 32:52.420
I'm worried.

32:53.070 --> 32:54.070
What should we do?

32:56.030 --> 32:56.660
How about

32:56.660 --> 32:57.870
we go look for her?

32:58.790 --> 32:59.310
Okay.

33:00.030 --> 33:00.890
Let's split up.

33:01.870 --> 33:02.400
Let's go.

33:05.750 --> 33:08.270
The plates are positioned right.

33:08.270 --> 33:11.070
The fertility blessings
are also placed correctly.

33:11.070 --> 33:13.550
But how many incense sticks
should we burn?

33:14.210 --> 33:15.190
Shouldn't it be 3?

33:15.190 --> 33:17.590
Right, so why did you place
a whole handful?

33:18.510 --> 33:20.110
What are you groaning about?

33:31.830 --> 33:32.750
Sir,

33:32.900 --> 33:35.110
I don't mean anything else.

33:35.460 --> 33:36.590
I just...

33:36.980 --> 33:38.980
Seeing the decorations today,

33:39.590 --> 33:41.460
it must be a wedding day.

33:42.900 --> 33:44.750
In that case,

33:45.350 --> 33:47.220
having a blade at my neck

33:47.660 --> 33:49.550
isn't very auspicious, right?

34:02.420 --> 34:04.420
I think it's better now.

34:04.420 --> 34:05.660
It's festive.

34:06.650 --> 34:07.690
Let me go!

34:07.790 --> 34:08.710
Let me go!

34:09.790 --> 34:10.790
Where is this?

34:13.739 --> 34:14.679
Tian Xing?

34:15.350 --> 34:16.460
Why are we here?

34:22.380 --> 34:24.110
I am an official of Nine Cities.

34:24.540 --> 34:26.670
Do you know you are committing a crime?

34:27.350 --> 34:28.280
Brother-in-law,

34:28.280 --> 34:31.239
your clothes are the perfect shade of red.

34:31.270 --> 34:33.080
Today is an auspicious day!

34:35.150 --> 34:36.880
Can someone explain this to me?

34:37.090 --> 34:38.150
What's happening?

34:38.380 --> 34:39.060
You,

34:39.060 --> 34:40.060
explain it to him.

34:42.580 --> 34:43.420
Me?

34:43.969 --> 34:45.010
I'll explain.

34:45.030 --> 34:46.719
I'll explain it to him.

34:47.630 --> 34:50.190
Looking at this scene, the decorations,

34:50.870 --> 34:52.969
and your red outfit,

34:53.110 --> 34:53.980
Tian Xing,

34:54.100 --> 34:55.020
today...

34:55.940 --> 34:57.670
might be your wedding day.

34:58.750 --> 34:59.900
Brother-in-law!

34:59.900 --> 35:01.960
Everything here is set up perfectly.

35:02.190 --> 35:03.500
After the wedding ceremony,

35:03.500 --> 35:06.330
you'll have to call us
your brothers-in-law.

35:06.540 --> 35:07.710
Brothers-in-law?

35:07.710 --> 35:08.770
What's happening?

35:09.780 --> 35:11.580
Sir, let him go first.

35:11.600 --> 35:13.030
We can talk this over.

35:13.060 --> 35:14.260
Let's talk this over.

35:15.500 --> 35:16.790
Excuse me, sir,

35:17.150 --> 35:19.020
how should I address you?

35:19.020 --> 35:21.520
Don't ask how to address me.

35:21.830 --> 35:24.500
You should ask how to address us.

35:24.790 --> 35:25.500
We are

35:25.500 --> 35:27.220
the famous brothers in Yong City—

35:27.220 --> 35:27.510
Wei!

35:27.540 --> 35:27.900
Meng!

35:27.930 --> 35:28.470
Gang!

35:28.560 --> 35:29.120
Yi!

35:32.300 --> 35:33.900
Wei, Meng, Gang, and Yi?

35:35.630 --> 35:36.750
Well, sirs,

35:36.940 --> 35:38.500
I have a question for you.

35:39.230 --> 35:40.380
People say

35:40.380 --> 35:42.640
marriage requires a matchmaker's word.

35:42.940 --> 35:44.460
So is there a matchmaker?

35:44.460 --> 35:45.380
And where is the marriage certificate?

35:45.380 --> 35:47.150
We don't have a matchmaker's word,

35:47.150 --> 35:49.210
nor a matchmaker, nor a certificate.

35:50.020 --> 35:51.380
You have nothing?

35:52.230 --> 35:53.940
But there should be a bride, right?

35:53.940 --> 35:54.980
Where is the bride?

35:54.980 --> 35:56.230
Without a bride, how can we

35:56.230 --> 35:58.190
proceed with the wedding ceremony?

35:58.190 --> 35:59.190
Right, right.

35:59.220 --> 36:01.230
How can I get married without a bride?

36:01.230 --> 36:02.230
Brother-in-law.

36:02.800 --> 36:03.600
Just you wait.

36:09.220 --> 36:11.110
We brothers are mighty, strong,

36:11.270 --> 36:13.100
handsome, and extremely smart.

36:13.100 --> 36:15.360
And our sister is extremely beautiful.

36:15.600 --> 36:16.660
In all of Yong City,

36:16.670 --> 36:18.860
she is among the most beautiful.

36:20.270 --> 36:22.670
Look how beautiful these eyes are.

36:25.570 --> 36:26.530
Aren't they?

36:28.710 --> 36:30.870
You... you called this beautiful?

36:35.420 --> 36:37.870
No! No!

36:37.870 --> 36:39.320
Yong City is known for its beauties.

36:39.320 --> 36:41.230
Yong City is known for its beauties.

36:41.230 --> 36:42.500
Thank you, sirs,

36:42.500 --> 36:44.100
for appreciating Tian Xing.

36:44.230 --> 36:45.750
He knows how lucky he is.

36:45.750 --> 36:46.980
How about this, sirs?

36:46.980 --> 36:48.500
Let these two guys

36:48.570 --> 36:49.870
put down their blades first.

36:49.870 --> 36:51.190
And I'll go talk to Tian Xing.

36:51.190 --> 36:53.150
He listens to me. I'll persuade him.

36:53.150 --> 36:55.190
There's no need. After the wedding today,

36:55.190 --> 36:57.250
he'll be the son-in-law of Yong City.

36:57.310 --> 36:59.350
Tomorrow,
he'll return to Yong City with us.

36:59.350 --> 37:00.500
Return to Yong City?

37:00.900 --> 37:02.830
But Tian Xing
is a newly appointed academician.

37:02.830 --> 37:04.540
How can he leave Ling'an so casually?

37:04.540 --> 37:06.500
His Excellency said he can. What's wrong?

37:06.500 --> 37:07.430
His Excellency?

37:07.940 --> 37:10.230
Who are you talking about?

37:10.980 --> 37:12.230
Say no more.

37:12.230 --> 37:13.230
Brother-in-law,

37:13.230 --> 37:15.900
just follow the arrangement
of your brothers-in-law.

37:15.900 --> 37:17.870
How can we treat marriage so casually?

37:17.870 --> 37:19.540
Why would I go to Yong City with you?

37:19.540 --> 37:21.940
A transfer
requires the Governor's approval.

37:21.940 --> 37:22.900
Yes.

37:22.900 --> 37:23.870
Marriage

37:23.870 --> 37:25.150
cannot be treated as a joke.

37:25.150 --> 37:25.980
How about this?

37:25.980 --> 37:27.020
Let's take our time to plan it.

37:27.020 --> 37:27.630
Let me go fir—

37:27.630 --> 37:29.380
Why are you nagging so much?

37:29.420 --> 37:30.240
So annoying.

37:31.280 --> 37:33.060
The auspicious time has come.
Let's proceed with the wedding!

37:33.060 --> 37:33.460
Come on, come on.

37:33.460 --> 37:34.790
Let's do it.

37:39.710 --> 37:40.150
No!

37:40.670 --> 37:41.100
No!

37:41.150 --> 37:41.630
No!

37:41.630 --> 37:42.580
Shouting is useless.

37:42.580 --> 37:43.060
Come on.

37:43.670 --> 37:45.330
First bow to Heaven and Earth!

37:45.460 --> 37:47.380
No! No!

37:49.060 --> 37:50.580
Second bow to the parents!

37:52.340 --> 37:53.860
No! No!

37:55.520 --> 37:57.520
Husband and wife, bow to each other!

37:57.680 --> 37:59.160
No! No! No!

37:59.190 --> 38:01.190
Husband and wife, bow to each other!

38:02.190 --> 38:04.520
Perform the cross-cupped wine ceremony!

38:15.260 --> 38:15.900
Brother-in-law,

38:15.900 --> 38:17.710
hurry up and drink the wedding wine.

38:17.710 --> 38:18.670
Brothers!

38:18.670 --> 38:20.580
Help our brother-in-law drink the wine!

38:20.580 --> 38:22.100
I won't drink it! I won't drink it!

38:22.100 --> 38:24.070
Once you drink the wine,
the ceremony is complete.

38:24.070 --> 38:25.330
-Tie up his hands!
-No!

38:27.360 --> 38:29.040
Fan Yun, what should we do?

38:33.350 --> 38:35.680
This little girl is Fan Yun?

38:44.230 --> 38:44.900
You...

38:45.190 --> 38:46.190
I am Tian Yue.

38:48.830 --> 38:49.380
I...

38:50.940 --> 38:52.460
So you are Fan Yun?

38:52.870 --> 38:55.070
Then don't blame us for being impolite.

38:56.350 --> 38:58.270
No killing! No killing!

38:58.270 --> 38:59.580
It's unlucky!

38:59.630 --> 39:01.060
It's precisely because it's an
auspicious day that we should...

39:01.060 --> 39:02.420
Killing draws blood!

39:02.420 --> 39:03.580
It's very troublesome to clean up!

39:03.580 --> 39:05.460
That's right. Shi Meng is right.

39:05.460 --> 39:07.390
It's very troublesome to clean up!

39:08.190 --> 39:09.230
Get out of here!

39:09.230 --> 39:10.830
The moon waxes and wanes!

39:10.830 --> 39:12.430
Tian Yue, drink the wine now!

39:14.710 --> 39:15.980
Brother!

39:17.100 --> 39:18.330
Put it down!

39:41.310 --> 39:42.350
Tian Yue!

39:42.900 --> 39:45.300
As the top candidate
in the selection exam,

39:45.390 --> 39:47.120
why would I be friends with you?

39:47.730 --> 39:49.990
Brother-in-law, what's wrong with you?

40:02.190 --> 40:03.500
Don't let them escape!

40:03.500 --> 40:04.150
Let's go!

40:13.750 --> 40:14.380
Boss.

40:14.790 --> 40:16.750
Today, the gates of Ling'an City
were suddenly closed,

40:16.750 --> 40:18.560
leaving only the south gate open.

40:18.560 --> 40:19.750
This has made it difficult
for our Juyun Pavilion's goods

40:19.750 --> 40:20.880
to come in and go out.

40:21.150 --> 40:21.830
I'm afraid

40:21.830 --> 40:23.540
they will be delayed for a while.

40:23.540 --> 40:24.630
So...

40:24.630 --> 40:25.320
Got it.

40:26.940 --> 40:28.350
So I went to ask around.

40:28.740 --> 40:29.700
Actually...

40:29.750 --> 40:31.210
What's there to ask about?

40:31.650 --> 40:32.680
The city gates were built

40:32.680 --> 40:34.410
to be opened and closed anyway.

40:34.980 --> 40:36.580
Can't you see I'm checking the accounts?

40:36.580 --> 40:37.580
I need some quiet.

40:38.100 --> 40:39.630
If there's nothing else, you may leave.

40:39.630 --> 40:40.420
Wait.

40:40.420 --> 40:43.020
It's said that some nobles from Yong City

40:43.220 --> 40:44.350
kidnapped someone.

40:48.500 --> 40:50.090
They can kidnap whoever they want.

40:50.090 --> 40:51.580
Why do you have so much nonsense
to say today?

40:51.580 --> 40:52.750
They kidnapped Fan Yun.

40:52.750 --> 40:53.230
That is all for my report.

40:53.230 --> 40:54.560
I will take my leave now.

41:11.710 --> 41:12.910
Excuse me! Excuse me!

41:15.350 --> 41:16.150
Tian Xing!

41:16.980 --> 41:17.900
Tian Yue!

41:18.380 --> 41:20.020
Are you Tian Xing or Tian Yue right now?

41:20.020 --> 41:21.020
I am Tian Xing.

41:21.580 --> 41:23.040
There are too many of them!

41:25.500 --> 41:26.060
Oh no!

41:26.060 --> 41:27.260
Hurry! Hurry! Hurry!

41:29.460 --> 41:31.230
Here! Here! Here!

41:34.380 --> 41:35.380
Let's go!

41:38.270 --> 41:39.110
This way!

41:52.150 --> 41:53.940
Make way! Make way! Over here!

41:53.940 --> 41:55.540
Hurry, hurry! Over here!

41:58.350 --> 41:59.750
Where are you running to?

42:01.630 --> 42:03.310
You little girl,

42:03.310 --> 42:05.190
you can really run.

42:24.670 --> 42:25.540
Lou Qiyan?

42:27.870 --> 42:29.630
Today is a good day,

42:33.060 --> 42:35.150
because it's the day you die.

42:36.350 --> 42:38.020
Just you guys?

42:38.020 --> 42:39.480
Look how arrogant you are!

42:50.980 --> 42:53.150
It's too dangerous here!

42:53.150 --> 42:55.940
We need to find another place to live!

42:55.940 --> 42:58.900
I heard there is a man
named Wei Rong in Gao City

42:58.900 --> 43:00.100
who is skilled
in both literature and martial arts

43:00.100 --> 43:01.760
and plays the flute very well.

43:02.100 --> 43:03.610
I heard that man

43:03.630 --> 43:05.540
dresses with great taste,

43:05.940 --> 43:07.740
much better than that Tian Xing.

43:07.940 --> 43:08.590
No.

43:08.790 --> 43:10.630
I want to be his brother-in-law!

43:10.630 --> 43:11.420
Right!

43:11.420 --> 43:12.270
-Me too!
-Me too!

43:12.270 --> 43:12.790
He has great taste!

43:12.790 --> 43:14.630
I never thought

43:14.630 --> 43:16.460
that on my first trip to Ling'an City,

43:16.460 --> 43:18.090
I'd be captured in broad daylight

43:18.090 --> 43:20.630
by the Shadow Slay League!

43:20.630 --> 43:23.350
Public security in Ling'an is terrible.

43:23.380 --> 43:24.910
I want to go home.

43:26.900 --> 43:27.900
The horses are ready.

43:27.900 --> 43:28.870
Go now.

43:31.020 --> 43:32.060
Okay.

43:32.060 --> 43:33.270
Tian Xing, let's go.
